CREATING DAX MEASURES 10

1. Create a 'Measures Table'


You will need to enter the DAX measures below one by one. The first two have been done in the gif shown.

1.   Class Score

.ClassScore% =

            VAR AvgClassScore = AVERAGE(vw_QS_MetricsDashboard_ClassManagement[ClassScore_Total])

    Return

            DIVIDE(AvgClassScore,5)

2. Note:   Format to percentage    to 2 decimal places    

  Instructor Score

.InstructorScore% =

        VAR AvgInstructorScore = AVERAGE(vw_QS_MetricsDashboard_ClassManagement[InstructorScore_Total])

RETURN

        DIVIDE(AvgInstructorScore,5)

3.   Impact

.Impact = [.InstructorScore%]- [.ClassScore%]     


Note:   Format to percentage    to 2 decimal places        

4.   Impact Arrow

.ArrowForImpact = SWITCH(TRUE(),[.InstructorScore%] > [.ClassScore%],UNICHAR(9650),

                 [.InstructorScore%] <[.ClassScore%],UNICHAR(9660))

5.   Impact Color

.ArrowImpactColor = SWITCH(TRUE(), [.InstructorScore%]> [.ClassScore%],"#008000",

                [.InstructorScore%] < [.ClassScore%], "#B20000")

 

 

6.   Total Class Sections Count

.TotalClassSections = SUM(vw_QS_MetricsDashboard_ClassManagement[Class_Duration])/180

7.  

Rolling 6 Months Average

.6MonthRollingImpactAverage =

VAR PercentAvg6MonthClassScore =

                                DIVIDE(

                                        CALCULATE(

                                                    AVERAGE(vw_QS_MetricsDashboard_ClassManagement[ClassScore_Total]

                                                            ),

                                                           

                                        DATESINPERIOD('Date'[Date],LASTDATE('Date'[Date]), -6, MONTH),  REMOVEFILTERS(Classes[ClassName]))

                                        , 5)

                               

                                       

VAR PercentAvg6MonthInstructorScore =

                                DIVIDE(

                                        CALCULATE(

                                                    AVERAGE(vw_QS_MetricsDashboard_ClassManagement[InstructorScore_Total]

                                                            ),

                                                           

                                        DATESINPERIOD('Date'[Date],LASTDATE('Date'[Date]), -6, MONTH),REMOVEFILTERS(Classes[ClassName]))

                                        , 5)

                                       

Return

 PercentAvg6MonthInstructorScore - PercentAvg6MonthClassScore

 

8.   Rolling 6 Month Arrow

.ArrowFor6MONTH = IF([.6MonthRollingImpactAverage]>=0,UNICHAR(9650), UNICHAR(9660))

9.   Rolling 6 Month Color

.ArrowColor6Month = IF([.6MonthRollingImpactAverage]>=0,"Green","#B20000")    




Rename the measures table and delete 'Column 1'
